המחלמ...אל / Nation...war (Isaiah 2:4)./PR

/PR

What do I desire for my country? How do I vision the land I love?/PR


Let it be a land where knowledge is free,/PR

Where the mind is without fear, and men and women hold their heads

high,/PR

Where words come out from the depth of truth,/PR

Where the world has not been broken up into fragments by narrow

domestic walls;/PR

Where tireless striving stretches its arms toward perfection,/PR

Where the clear stream of reason has not lost its way in the dreamy

desert sand of dead habit,/PR

Where the mind is led forward into ever-widening thought and action,/PR

Into that heaven of freedom let my country awake./PR

